englishTranslation: Brothers Today we are with a young man who has become a whole new leaf

hebrewFromSub: שרק עזב את הכלא וכבר נתן בנדיבות מהמלאי הדל שלו
englishFromSub: He has only just left prison yet he has given generously of his meagre store
englishTranslation: Who has just left prison and has already given generously from his meager inventory

englishFromSub: Friend will you step up beside me and bear witness
englishTranslation: - A friend will come up beside me and carry a witness
-I do not believe in sin -Everyone sins

hebrewFromSub: -אחי תירתע אתה עומד מול סכנה גדולה
englishFromSub: We know Brother be warned you stand in great danger
englishTranslation: - My brother will be deterred. You are facing great danger

englishFromSub: I thought like you once sir but now I've learned better
englishTranslation: - I once thought like you sir but I got stronger

hebrewFromSub: -אנשים טובים רק אם תיתן להם הזדמנות
englishFromSub: People are good if you give them the chance
englishTranslation: -Good people only if you give them a chance

englishFromSub: We've got to start with humanity
englishTranslation: One has to start with humanity
